@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lxxdqu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.24)) + ((v2 + 0.90 * v2 + 0.68) - (v0 + 0.03 / v0 + 0.57)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.94) * ((v1 + 0.72 / v0 + 0.57) / v0))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v1) * ((v0 + 0.80 + v0 + 0.40) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.75)))
    data[tid] = v0
